    "The lighter-weight Claude Sonnet 4 offers almost the same performance at lower compute cost.",
    "Both models feature an \"Extended Thinking\" mode that turns on in-depth reasoning capabilities.",
    "Claude can also be easily connected to external apps such as email applications.",
